The distribution of the new genus/species is given in 
<figureCitation id="1334AAEAEF24FFDFFC0FA11CFBC1FD07" box="[956,1038,620,645]" captionStart="FIGURE 15" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1339,1361]" captionText="FIGURE 15. Distribution of Spazigasteroides gen. nov. in China." pageId="4" pageNumber="234">
Fig. 
<number id="3DC7A448EF24FFDFFC5CA11CFBC1FD07" box="[1007,1038,620,645]" pageId="4" pageNumber="234" value="15.0">15</number>
</figureCitation>
